text.section:
To qualify for a license, an applicant shall satisfy the Secretary that the proposed private group home:
Is needed;
Is compatible with the nature and character of the area involved;
Is near transportation facilities;
Meets or, on completion, will meet the requirements of this subtitle and the rules and regulations that the Secretary adopts under this subtitle; and
Meets or, on completion, will meet all general zoning requirements that apply to the site and that relate to:
The height and size of any buildings that are involved;
The land that may be covered or occupied;
The size of yards that require open space;
The density of population; and
The use of the land and buildings.
